          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Secret Character -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After entering the following code press R1 at the character select screen for the secret character.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Shinobi -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Beat the game without using any continues. You also need to be at a difficulty of two or three stars, and fight Shinobi to beat the game. Then when you select a character, press R1 or R2 to select Shinobi.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Genichiro -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Beat the game with Shinobu without continuing.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Ichiko -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Obtain 14 wins in Survival mode after unlocking Tetsuko & Genichiro.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Tetsuko -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Beat the game with Asuka or Karina without continuing.</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite HP Player 1 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8005B00C 4B00</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock all characters -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8005A42C 0007</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
